title: Mini Bautista hangs with Real-Life Bautista before ALCS Game 4
text:
Mini Bautista, world’s greatest Blue Jays fan , made an appearance at Rogers Centre on Tuesday, in advance of Toronto’s ALCS Game 4 against the Kansas City Royals . 
He snagged this photo with Actual Jose Bautista, naturally. Can you tell them apart? 
— MLB (@MLB) October 20, 2015 
I would like to think that Mini Bautista is good luck for Toronto, but like five minutes after I started writing this post, the Royals had already taken the lead. 
So … uh … are there any other adorable children dressed up like Toronto ballplayers out there? What about a Mini Kevin Pillar? Come on, the Blue Jays might need all the help they can get.
